title: It's a fantastic addition to my tech arsenal!
body: I recently purchased the COSTAR 33W Dual Port Fast Charger QC/PD, and I couldn't be happier with my purchase! This charger is an absolute game-changer for anyone looking to charge multiple devices quickly and efficiently.  The dual-port design is incredibly convenient, allowing me to charge both my USB and Type C devices simultaneously without any compromise in charging speed. Whether it's my smartphone, tablet, or any other gadgets, this charger handles them all with ease.  The fast charging capability is a real game-changer, reducing the time it takes to power up my devices significantly. I can now get a substantial battery boost in just a short amount of time, which is perfect for my busy lifestyle.  The build quality is top-notch, and I can tell that this charger is built to last. It feels sturdy and reliable, giving me the confidence that it will stand the test of time.  Overall, the COSTAR 33W Dual Port Fast Charger QC/PD is an exceptional product that delivers on its promises. It has made my life so much easier, and I highly recommend it to anyone in need of a reliable and fast charger for their devices.

title: 'Think before you buy - Explanation below'
body: '1. First thing first it\'s small and lightweight 2. You can charge two devices simultaneously 3. It\'s not an original charger. So think twice before buying. 4. I explored that it starts with "Fast Charging" and after a few minutes it changes its mode to "Standard Charging". So if you are thinking to buy it for charging your supported phone it won\'t help you. My phone supports Fast Charging 33W. But this device working like a normal charger. 5. No support for the device is available. If you face any issue with the product you are gone.'
